description._content: Description: Group of Chinese coolies at Raydh (on the level land suitable for Mill or Depôt. Location: Raydh, Borneo ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Chinese eating House at Raydh (77m) on the level land suitable for Mill or Depôt. Location: Raydh, Borneo ------------------------------------------------------ Description: The village of Raydh on opposite side of stream from the level piece suitable for Mill or Depôt. Location: Raydh, Borneo ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Raydh Hill (1400-1500 ft): another view from the level Ground above Raydh stream. Location: Raydh, Borneo ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/526. This description, taken from the original image, may contain terminology that may no longer be acceptable in contemporary discourse.
